New and Changed Objects in Quote and Order Capture

Store information about the type of a sales transaction. Use the new SalesTransactionType object.
Also, use these new objects: 
  - SalesTransactionTypeOwnerSharingRule
  - SalesTransactionTypeShare
Use the new fields:
  - ValidationResult (Quote)
  - ValidationResult (Order)
  - OrchestrationSbmsStatus (Order)
  - CalculationStatus (Order)
  - CustomProductName (OrderItem)
  - SubscriptionTerm (OrderItem)
  - Status and DocumentTemplate (QuoteDocument)
 
Use the new objects:
  - ContractItemPrice
  - ContractItemPriceHistory
Use the fields on the existing object: 
  - PricingSource, RenewalTerm2, and RenewalTermUnit (Contract)
